---
title: Eggy Sausage Flatbreads with Tomato and Basil
description: Pizza for breakfast just went from “oh no” to “oh yeah!” This recipe is the opposite of a leftover slice: it’s piping hot, toasty, and loaded with delicious, morning-friendly toppings like lightly sweet breakfast sausage and sunny-side-up eggs. But since it is still a pizza, there are tomatoes, cheese, and basil, too, just in case you still wanted a taste of margherita in the AM.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/eggy-sausage-flatbreads-c1b84913.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/eggy-sausage-flatbreads-72d5ea35.pdf
